title: Cable Matters Inline Passive Power Injector over Ethernet
feature: PASSIVE PoE INJECTOR KIT provides in line power over a Cat 5, 5e, 6 Ethernet network cable to an IP camera, IP phone, wireless access point and more; Enables non PoE equipped devices to be powered over a single network cable; Allows a more flexible position for an IP device

PoE POWER is sent from the original AC power adapter of your device over a network cable and then split out to provide power at the remote end; IP device power connector has the common 5.5 x 2.1mm center negative male barrel; Powers devices from 15 to 150 feet depending on the voltage of the power supply and quality of the network cable
STURDY CABLE CONSTRUCTION includes gold-plated connectors, 24 AWG wire, an industry standard fire retardant jacket, and molded strain relief connectors

PoE POWER SPLITTER uses pins 1-2 and 3-6 for data; Pins 4-5 7-8 are used for power; Supports Fast Ethernet speeds required by most IP cameras and phones; Gigabit Ethernet is not supported since two pairs are used for power
